Package com.shopgun.android.sdk.api

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Endpoints
    This class contains a sub-set of paths needed to request data from the ShopGun API, and has methods to generate paths, that dependent on information from objects (id's e.t.c).
    MetaKeys
    This class contains a sub-set of strings that ShopGun uses as keys for the meta-object, found on Shoppinglist.getMeta(), and ShoppinglistItem.getMeta().
    Parameters
    This class contains sub-set of strings, that ShopGun API v2 uses as parameters, for queries to the API.
    SortBy
    This class contains a sub-set of strings that ShopGun uses for sorting lists queries.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Environment
    The Environment contains information on how (and where) to contact the ShopGun API.
    ThemeEnvironment
